    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you channel the darkest emotions and focus them into a burst of magical menace. Each creature of your choice within 30 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw if it can see you. On a failed save, the target is <strong>frightened</strong> of you for 1 minute. If a creature frightened by this effect ends its turn more than 30 feet away from you, it can attempt another Wisdom saving throw to end the effect on it.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-HDMDT3SOaYqoUWbT\"><p><em>Note: When you add this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Channel Divinity.</em></p></section>",
